VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT Hive\.openBox\s*\(|Hive\.openLazyBox\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:encryptionCipher|HiveAesCipher|encryptionKey
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Hive boxes opened without an encryption cipher for sensitive data storage.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Hive Box Opened Without Encryption.
